    </div>
    <div id="product-navbar">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#a" id="over" onclick="overview()">Overview</a>
        <li><a href="#a" onclick="dates_prices()">Dates and prices</a>
        <li><a href="#a" onclick="tour()">Tour</a>
        <li><a href="#a" onclick="reviews()">Reviews</a>
      </ul>
      <div id="overview">
        <p>The park covers 14,750 square kilometres (5,700 sq mi)[7] of grassland plains, savanna, riverine forest, and woodlands. The park lies in northwestern Tanzania, bordered to the north by the Kenyan border, where it is continuous with the Maasai Mara National Reserve. To the southeast of the park is the Ngorongoro Conservation Area, to the southwest lies Maswa Game Reserve, to the west are the Ikorongo and Grumeti Game Reserves, and to the northeast and east lies the Loliondo Game Control Area. Together, these areas form the larger Serengeti ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
      <div id="dates-prices">
        <p>The Dates and prices</p>
      </div>
      <div id="tour">
        <p>The Tour</p>
      </div>
      <div id="reviews">
        <p>The Reviews</p>
      </div>
